fit_hab0.desc: Regular Exercise - At least 30 minutes physical activity

fit_hab1.desc: Balanced Nutrition - Consume a well-rounded diet

fit_hab2.desc: Adequate Sleep - Sleep 7-9 hours each night

fit_hab3.desc: Hydration - Drink at least 2l of water a day

fin_hab0.desc: Budgeting - Spend some time each day to review you spending

fin_hab1.desc: Saving - Set aside a some money for rainy days

rel_hab0.desc: Gratitude - Express appreciation for the people an things in your life

rel_hab1.desc: Quality Time - Spend Time with those you Love

rel_hab2.desc: Communication - Improve your social skills by speaking to a stranger everyday

acc_hab0.desc: Continuous Learning - Learn something new everyday

acc_hab1.desc: Time Management - Plan the next day, focus your intent on a few critical tasks

acc_hab2.desc: Goal Setting - Redefine and look over your goals everyday

acc_hab3.desc: Networking - Build a strong professional network
